<main>
    <section class="row" aria-labelledby="aspnetTitle">

        <h1 id="title" class="custom-heading">
            <span class="bold-text">Welcome to EventUp</span> <br>
            <span class="cursive-text">The Complete Solution for Your Events!</span>
        </h1>

        <br />
        <p class="paragraph">Discover the easiest and most exciting way to plan your events. With EventUp, gone are the days when organizing an event or hiring a specialist felt tedious. Now, you can do it all yourself with a few simple clicks.</p>
        <br />
        <span class="questions-content1">Why choose us? </span> <br>
        <br />
       
        <div class="column" style="background-color: #680747; ">
