            <p class="column-content">Connect directly with reliable service providers. EventUp makes communication easy, ensuring you get exactly what you desire without the hassle.</p>
        </div>


        <span class="questions-content2">Are you an event service provider? </span> <br>

        <p class="paragraph">
            Join EventUp and expand your reach. Become the preferred choice for those looking to plan the best events.
        </p>

        <p><a href="@Url.Action("Register", "Account")" class="btn btn-primary">Register here </a></p>
    </section>
    <br />

